name: Planet Zenon NFT
description:
The year 2021. 1st Nov.  Still 19 days until Planet Zenon really catches fire. 

My soul mate and alien connector; uncle nut...mysteriously has a connection to this Planet Zenon.  He is a believer.  

I want to inscribe here, into the blockchain forever...what he believes.

$ZNN is coming. Zenon will change lives. Zenon.network is something to lead humanity to greatness. 

End of transmission...


I'm not sure what it all means, but I know if he said it, it must mean something big for many people. 

With much gratitude.


Starseed
